{"tid":1577864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post 新屋嶺要做翻啲嘢先得","createTime":"2019-09-18T02:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T04:54:54.000Z","uid":52779,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fc709e7df06fe4b707ce5ad7ed68ac0229bd420e","tid":1577864,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"成日聽人講新屋嶺女義士俾人輪<br />\n又有好多ching 嗌佢地出嚟講翻件事<br />\n但事實上呢班女義士身心靈都已經受到好多傷害<br />\n同埋本身嗌受害人出嚟已經係二次傷害<br />\n藍絲咁鍾意作故仔<br />\n就算真係俾人姦都好<br />\n講啲說話都會好難聽<br />\n企喺心靈傷害好重嘅手足嗰邊<br />\n我唔贊成佢地企出嚟<br />\n但咁唔代表我地冇野可以做<br />\n我地可以做嘅野好簡單：<br />\n文宣！文宣！文宣！<br />\n簽聯署！簽聯署！簽聯署！<br />\n煲大新屋嶺，721，831<br />\n呢三樣野絕對係港共嘅春袋<br />\n文宣方向721，831一直都冇錯，keep going <br />\n但新屋嶺文宣略嫌少咗啲，我建議文宣可以講翻：<br />\n1. 本身新屋嶺係裝咩犯<br />\n2. 蘋果咪訪問過我在新屋嶺的32小時嘅，放大翻啲野<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_692387_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_692387_0&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5Phh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=2c40dc54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_692387_0&h=46510dfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_692387_0</a> <br />\n3. 北區醫院醫護講嘅野，唔好開名喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190902/60001252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190902%2F60001252&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5Phh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=127f07bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190902%2F60001252&h=41cda8ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190902/60001252</a><br />\n4. 建議民間記者會可以用新屋嶺做主題，我地有知情權知道點解會去新屋嶺⋯搵到律師證實去新屋嶺係唔合理就更加好喇<br />\n5. 諗翻句口號，遊行，鳩叫果時嗌下，好似721唔見人，831打死人呢啲咁，有口號廢老都識嗌喇⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTBad2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTBad2W.jpg&h=2447d6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OKyf9Bh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOKyf9Bh.jpg&h=7ed907b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLFeFHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLFeFHY.jpg&h=5b9fec2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯署嘅話咧，其實有ching 開過post <br />\n突發！！ 新屋嶺要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1575390\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1575390</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n暫時係咁多⋯有更加多建議可以再加⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721，831，新屋嶺"},{"pid":"544fe1c000380dfc2057396d80cc6ddd28e43c6c","tid":1577864,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:00:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10de3ad83b3eda1c49e993c4db4878a41cf9b41d","tid":1577864,"uid":162783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:03:44.000Z","msg":"張圖貼滿佢"},{"pid":"8d1ecf19de61b6f5dcdbea38725e743bddfbeb82","tid":1577864,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10de3ad83b3eda1c49e993c4db4878a41cf9b41d","tid":1577864,"uid":162783,"